comments: LaVine (CHI) places his hand momentarily on Butler's (MIA) side and immediately removes his hand as LaVine begins his upward shooting motion.
Lowry (MIA) legally contests DeRozan's (CHI) jump shot attempt.
White (CHI) extends his forearm into Butler's (MIA) path and delivers contact that affects his FOM off ball.
Robinson (MIA) establishes himself in Vucevic's (CHI) path and absorbs the contact during the screen.
Caruso (CHI) jumps forward into Butler's (MIA) body and initiates contact as he defends the jump shot attempt.
Lowry (MIA) makes clean contact with the ball as he defends LaVine's (CHI) drive.
Caruso (CHI) is already in Butler's (MIA) path and absorbs the contact during the pick.
Robinson (MIA) moves laterally into Caruso's (CHI) path and initiates body contact prior to Caruso's gather that affects his SQBR.
Caruso (CHI) is already in Adebayo's (MIA) path when contact occurs and he absorbs the contact during the screen.
Lowry (MIA) is already in Caruso's (CHI) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
White (CHI) legally contests Butler's (MIA) jump shot attempt.
Caruso (CHI) is firming up over his left leg in Jaquez Jr.'s (MIA) path and he absorbs the contact during the pick.
Jaquez Jr. (MIA) turns into DeRozan's (CHI) body and initiates contact that affects his ability to follow-through following the release of his jump shot.
Lowry (MIA) establishes himself in Caruso's (CHI) path and absorbs the contact during the pick.
Caruso (CHI) legally contests Butler's (MIA) jump shot attempt.
Butler (MIA) commits a take foul on DeRozan (CHI).
Craig (CHI) maintains verticality and marginal contact occurs as he contests Butler's (MIA) jump shot.
Lowry (MIA) extends his hand forward and makes contact with DeRozan's (CHI) arm.
